Text: I just have to say, great torrent. This is the only one I could find that had the reprised Ohio track and Belgium from AHYDD. Good job, zibbik.
not a full discography but is a good collection :)

Missing 4 Albums. 
Cell Mates (1996)
Tell Me When To Whoa (1998)
Bowling For Soup Goes To The Movies (2005)
Fishin' for Woos (Released after torrent - 2011)

Also incorrect release dates:
Bowling for soup 1994 not 1995
Rock on Honorable Ones!! 1997 not 1998

A re upload with the correct and missing data would be appreciated.
Don't take this the wrong way, just being informative.

CHANNEL NEO has a more complete discography, minus two bonus tracks. Less seeders, but you give and take. 

http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/4352845/BOWLING_FOR_SOUP_-_DISCOGRAPHY_[CHANNEL_NEO]
